The easiest way to use 3L on ChromeOS is to install the extension from
the Chrome Web Store:

https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/3l-keyboard-layout/bjapeaembccmkkkknjhjpjpajhdcoihh

If you wish to install/modify the sources:

1. Go to chrome://extensions. Use the toggle in the top right to
   enable "Developer mode."

2. Select "Load unpacked" and choose the "src" directory in this
   directory.

3. ...

4. Profit!
